{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"0679d0fe0adbdc8a55c6910338448203","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"MandalaChart already has 5 layers (Astrologia, Tântrica, I-Ching, Cabala, Odus) — but uses the data structure from `/api/akasha/mandala`, not the R-030 `calcular()` output. And it doesn't consume data.iching, data.odus, data.tantra, data.kabala, data.astrology from R-030 directly.\n\nLet me look at what the actual gap is. The current MandalaChart is good. F-203 says \"consume data.iching + data.odus + data.tantra + data.kabala + data.astrology no MandalaChart, 5 anéis com cor por Pilar\".\n\nLet me check what R-030 outputs and what /api/akasha/mandala outputs.","signature":"5aaa3112f90185c6da3c48e0e80c7196e25117f19dfc34d3523b0098067da5d2"}],"model":"MiniMax-M3","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"service_tier":"standard"},"service_tier":"standard","context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"44a294c9-7ecf-4f85-9b61-8e5a12793e2c","uuid":"8f4862ba-9806-49e2-9897-c20cedb98cf8"}
